item.title: 317 cache
item.dc:creator: @Scape-JAVA Scape-JAVA
item.description:
@Scape-JAVA wrote:

0.0.0.0 is a localhost.

And usually client sided, depends what client you’re using. Try looking for a string such as “server =” without the quotation marks, or just search the client for the localhost.
